  "3276050": {
    "name": "SpaceCraft",
    "steam_appid": 3276050,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276050/extras/294e3f87400f296a4f9ba3c05c5edc66.avif?t=1771889867\" width=1228 height=98 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276050/extras/fec2243ae361b58f9fa863f206738678.poster.avif?t=1771889867\" width=1170 height=418 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276050/extras/fec2243ae361b58f9fa863f206738678.webm?t=1771889867\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276050/extras/fec2243ae361b58f9fa863f206738678.mp4?t=1771889867\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>公元2350年。人类在研究一段被遗忘的古文明时，意外唤醒了能够自我复制、全自动的战斗机器人——“三足”。随之而来的是一场残酷的世纪大战，直到一场神秘的“H事件”彻底改写了战局。电光火石之间，人类的舰队几乎全军覆没，平衡被瞬间打破。<br><br>三足军团大举进攻联合行星，人类几乎无路可逃。就在此时，一段来自遥远星系的神秘代码传来，标示出一个隐藏传送门的坐标。作为最后的赌注，幸存者们穿越传送门，逃亡未知的星系，这片陌生的星系或许藏着人类生存的终极希望。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276050/extras/ac3200f9f5a37949e2021aa67198cb54.avif?t=1771889867\" width=1228 height=98 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276050/extras/2a6987b5bc6095660418edf93142f6eb.poster.avif?t=1771889867\" width=1170 height=418 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276050/extras/2a6987b5bc6095660418edf93142f6eb.webm?t=1771889867\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276050/extras/2a6987b5bc6095660418edf93142f6eb.mp4?t=1771889867\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>自由驰骋在浩瀚无垠的宇宙中，眼前是一片充满无限可能的星海。驾驶你的飞船穿梭于星系之间，踏足遍布行星、小行星带、废弃空间站与遗迹的神秘领域。借助超光速科技，你可以轻松跃迁，瞬间跨越宇宙的广袤距离。<br><br>实时掌控飞船，穿越深空与行星表面之间无缝切换。无论你是在扫描行星以搜寻珍稀资源，还是绘制遗失世界的星图，整个宇宙都任你探索。这里没有边界，只有等待你发现的未知。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276050/extras/1740a16a1142e666e79132b2eb3a3d85.avif?t=1771889867\" width=1228 height=98 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276050/extras/5fad38013c25aa1ddc9e50817afd4ed3.poster.avif?t=1771889867\" width=1170 height=418 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276050/extras/5fad38013c25aa1ddc9e50817afd4ed3.webm?t=1771889867\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276050/extras/5fad38013c25aa1ddc9e50817afd4ed3.mp4?t=1771889867\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>每一颗星球都蕴藏着丰富的自然资源，等待你去发掘与利用。在新星系中探索时，携带各式工具，提取原材料。扫描环境，利用飞船进行资源开采和收集，将这些原料精心打造成珍贵物资或飞船零部件，用于贸易或交易。<br><br>利用精密部件打造你的专属飞船。无论是灵活敏捷的小型舰，还是重载的太空货轮，每一块组件都将影响它的性能。你还可以购买其他玩家的设计图，快速组装属于自己的成品飞船。一旦设计完美的飞船，你也可以出售设计蓝图，让其他玩家驾驶你的杰作，驰骋星空。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276050/extras/9ef122c598440fe4a916d54b2ba69d46.avif?t=1771889867\" width=1228 height=98 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276050/extras/1f660bfe86488f6e77605d5836e882b3.poster.avif?t=1771889867\" width=1170 height=418 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276050/extras/1f660bfe86488f6e77605d5836e882b3.webm?t=1771889867\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276050/extras/1f660bfe86488f6e77605d5836e882b3.mp4?t=1771889867\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>在浩瀚的旅途中，不断提高效率，通过自动化推动事业扩张。在宇宙中建立并壮大你的基地。将行星上的前哨站打造成资源全自动的枢纽。<br><br>构建无人机和货运舰队，形成自动化的生产与运输网络，轻松管理采矿、资源提取和物流运作。从居住区到生产线，从能源管理到星际物流，优化和自动化每个环节。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276050/extras/92aae144707064885d0898463c974a92.avif?t=1771889867\" width=1228 height=98 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276050/extras/3acaed062045911e9b3655997533bf0c.poster.avif?t=1771889867\" width=1170 height=418 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276050/extras/3acaed062045911e9b3655997533bf0c.webm?t=1771889867\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276050/extras/3acaed062045911e9b3655997533bf0c.mp4?t=1771889867\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>宇宙暗流涌动，危险无处不在。流浪势力与太空海盗横行星系，随时准备伏击任何国王之人。迎战准备分为侦测、追踪和交锋三步：先在雷达上锁定敌方舰船，再发起追击，但他们可能会尝试逃脱。<br><br>战斗一触即发，你将结合直观的操控与深度机制，实时部署技能、监控热量水平。每次交锋都是一次策略博弈，你的抉择不仅决定胜负，还可能影响星际力量的分布，在银河中留下属于你的足迹。<br><br><i><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >战斗内容将在抢先体验期间加入。</h2></i><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276050/extras/64add4103619098219b5bc11de7873c7.avif?t=1771889867\" width=1228 height=98 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276050/extras/26b7f0bf484a384c57970c2b98068225.poster.avif?t=1771889867\" width=1170 height=418 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276050/extras/26b7f0bf484a384c57970c2b98068225.webm?t=1771889867\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276050/extras/26b7f0bf484a384c57970c2b98068225.mp4?t=1771889867\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>置身于一个由玩家行动塑造的星系。采矿、制作、交易资源和飞船部件；买卖设计蓝图，接受或提供服务、任务和合约。融入并适应宇宙经济，每一笔交易都会影响市场价格的波动。<br><br>真正的力量源于协作。创建或加入星际公司，在更大规模上展开合作。分配角色、划分任务，管理从小型舰队到庞大商业帝国的星际生产和物流，共同打造跨星际的商业网络。",
    "supported_languages": "英语, 法语, 德语, 西班牙语 - 西班牙, 波兰语, 葡萄牙语 - 巴西, 俄语, 简体中文",
